\contentsline {table}{\numberline {4.40}{\ignorespaces Top-level latency summary for \texttt {softmax\_top} at \SI {150}{\mega \hertz }. The minimum corresponds to $\texttt {size} = 1$ and the maximum to $\texttt {size} = \texttt {MAXSIZE} = 16$.}}{56}{table.caption.399}%
