\contentsline {table}{\numberline {4.50}{\ignorespaces Latency breakdown of \texttt {softmax\_ibert} ($\texttt {MAX\_SIZE} = 16$) at \SI {150}{\mega \hertz }. All loops are fully unrolled so HLS reports no per-loop trip count, and the breakdown is therefore given at the submodule level. AXI wrapper overhead covers the input and output burst transfers.}}{62}{table.caption.416}%
